{"lastModified":1776326162879,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Summer 2026 Operating Area: Greece - Aegean/Cyclades Sea, Greece - Ionian Sea\nWinter 2025/2026 Operating Area: Bermuda, British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, US Virgin Islands, Windward Islands\n\nStep aboard Mattea, remarkable 80 Sunreef Power launched in June 2025—a bold statement of contemporary yachting. With her distinctive turquoise hull and sleek profile, Mattea combines avant-garde design with refined comfort, promising an unforgettable escape on the water.\n\nCrafted for discerning travellers, Mattea strikes the perfect balance between elegance and functionality. Her expansive flybridge is tailored for outdoor living, featuring a BBQ station, oversized sunpads, and a hammock—ideal for soaking up the sun or enjoying a laid-back evening under the stars. A flexible lounging and dining area with a convertible table invites effortless entertaining.\n\nThe aft cockpit flows seamlessly into the luminous saloon, which opens fully to the exterior and offers sweeping views and natural light. A discreet garage holds an array of water toys, while the hydraulic swim platform can be transformed into a private beach club. The forward terrace completes the outdoor experience with its generous sunpads and a jacuzzi, perfect for unwinding in total privacy.\n\nInside, Mattea welcomes guests with a serene, modern interior. The master cabin is a sanctuary in soft grey tones, while three additional guest cabins, each with ensuite bathrooms, provide a harmonious blend of luxury and comfort. The galley-down configuration ensures seamless gourmet preparation, and the dedicated crew quarters uphold both service quality and guest privacy.\n\nEquipped with solar panels, Mattea is designed with sustainability in mind—delivering both performance and eco-conscious cruising. From its innovative layout to its upscale finishes, every aspect of Mattea is crafted to offer an elevated charter experience that redefines life at sea.","blueprint":{"name":"MATTEA","images":["/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::46abf350-57d5-11f0-999b-2bedb1b28dde/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::4c84fd80-57d5-11f0-999b-2bedb1b28dde/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::b1375750-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::6b17fc70-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::6b1b09b0-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::6b182380-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::6b178740-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::6b5f1790-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::73502c50-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::734fde30-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::73520110-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::734f6900-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::0c313760-3a1d-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::734eccc1-57d5-11f0-bed9-5d00d67e23fa/{imageVari